Matron Meng!

5
00:01:58,760 --> 00:01:59,440
Manager Fang,

6
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:01,919
please check.

7
00:02:03,239 --> 00:02:03,879
Matron Meng,

8
00:02:04,279 --> 00:02:04,879
you...

9
00:02:05,239 --> 00:02:06,040
Fool!

10
