Why did you address her as the matron?

11
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:11,520
I'll help you check.

12
00:02:23,199 --> 00:02:24,360
Today's vegetables

13
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,600
don't look fresh.

14
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:27,279
The vegetables aren't fresh.

15
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,039
Have you forgotten, Madam Meng?

16
00:02:29,839 --> 00:02:31,360
You used to say that fresh vegetables

17
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:32,919
should be cooked

18
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:35,039
within two hours after they were picked.

19
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:36,759
Sometimes, they arrived

20
00:02:36,759 --> 00:02:37,759
with dew drops on them.

21
00:02:38,759 --> 00:02:39,479
Look at these.

22
00:02:40,919 --> 00:02:41,440
Sorry.

23
00:02:41,919 --> 00:02:42,880
Please

24
00:02:43,399 --> 00:02:44,520
send another cart.

25
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,160
Manager Wen, but...

26
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:54,199
Stop slicing.

27
00:02:54,199 --> 00:02:54,759
Let's go.

28
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:56,479
Manager Wen bullied Madam Meng again.

29
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:09,800
Don't go.

30
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:18,759
Let me take this.

31
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:25,279
Given her temperament,

32
00:03:25,839 --> 00:03:27,240
Matron Meng doesn't need sympathy.

33
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,279
Work hard.

34
00:03:37,839 --> 00:03:38,720
Let me do it.

35
00:03:50,479 --> 00:03:51,559
Please observe

36
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,160
social hierarchy.

37
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:09,119
Let's go.

38
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,320
Yuehua.

39
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,279
Next time you see Matron Meng,

40
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:19,959
don't be so rude.

41
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:27,119
Directress Hu is temporarily in charge

42
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:29,959
