44
00:04:48,946 --> 00:04:53,679
[Xingyun Cottage]

45
00:04:53,679 --> 00:04:54,839
Miss Yao, you are here.

46
00:04:55,839 --> 00:04:56,799
Please wait.

47
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:57,720
Yes.

48
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,440
I'll wait.

49
00:04:58,559 --> 00:04:59,239
Official Yang.

50
