deliberately conceal this?

61
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,200
This...

62
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:03,839
If you don't wake up,

63
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,399
I'll kiss you.

64
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:19,920
Your Highness.

65
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,119
I breached the etiquette.

66
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:23,640
Please forgive me.

67
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,160
You have always been discourteous.

68
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,200
You fell asleep while delivering a meal.

69
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:30,799
Then you overstepped your bounds.

70
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:33,519
I had to carry you.

71
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,519
