72
00:07:37,399 --> 00:07:37,920
Men!

73
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:40,880
Give her 20 beatings.

74
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:42,320
Your Highness.

75
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:43,720
Your Highness.

76
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,399
Are you scared?

77
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:46,760
Look clearly.

78
00:07:47,399 --> 00:07:49,399
This is the way a master treats his servants.

79
00:08:14,399 --> 00:08:14,920
Chin up.

80
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:15,920
I dare not.

81
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:19,799
Lift your head.

82
00:08:19,799 --> 00:08:21,760
I order you to lift your chin up now.

83
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:26,440
Well?

84
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:36,599
Why did you fall asleep?

85
00:08:38,119 --> 00:08:38,919
I...

86
