91
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:51,960
I'll transfer you here.

92
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:53,039
No.

93
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,320
Permit me,

94
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,840
Your Highness,

95
00:08:59,039 --> 00:09:00,320
to remain there.

96
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,559
Alright,

97
00:09:04,039 --> 00:09:05,080
but you need to promise me this.

98
00:09:06,719 --> 00:09:07,400
From now on,

99
00:09:08,239 --> 00:09:10,599
you don't address yourself as a servant.

100
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:12,280
Tell me.

101
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:15,280
Why do you like being a cook?

102
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:18,520
Your Highness,

103
