when I was a child.

104
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:26,359
(She asked my tutor to be strict.)

105
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:28,840
(I go beaten for forgetting)

106
00:09:29,679 --> 00:09:30,760
(songs for the guqin.)

107
00:09:38,679 --> 00:09:39,400
At that time,

108
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:41,320
the kitchen

109
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,880
was my sanctuary.

110
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,280
It was small

111
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:46,280
and full of porcelain.

112
00:09:46,880 --> 00:09:48,119
She couldn't swing the rattan.

113
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,760
At the Imperial Food Service,

114
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,400
I spent my most relaxing

115
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,679
and happiest moments.

116
00:09:54,239 --> 00:09:55,000
There,

117
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:58,039
