118
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:01,039
I found the meaning of my existence.

119
00:10:04,039 --> 00:10:04,599
Your Highness,

120
00:10:05,599 --> 00:10:07,359
please let me spend more time there.

121
00:10:12,719 --> 00:10:13,400
I thought

122
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:16,880
your happiest time was in this study.

123
00:10:18,039 --> 00:10:19,119
