00:13:10,559 --> 00:13:11,119
Zijin.

150
00:13:11,559 --> 00:13:13,400
Did you compile the list of
herbal food from all dynasties?

151
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:13,960
Yes.

152
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:15,320
It'll be done by tomorrow.

153
00:13:17,679 --> 00:13:18,520
What is this?

154
00:13:20,599 --> 00:13:22,159
The Great Imperial Grandson's Consort

155
00:13:22,159 --> 00:13:23,719
tasted Zijin's food at the banquet

156
00:13:24,119 --> 00:13:25,479
and told Zijin to deliver a snack.

157
00:14:11,327 --> 00:14:12,675
[Taiji Hawthorn and Milk Cream]

158
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,880
A girl who makes such delicious food

159
00:14:53,400 --> 00:14:55,159
must be smart.

160
00:14:57,760 --> 00:14:58,599
Can you play weiqi?

161
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:16,719
Table Maid Yao,

162
00:15:17,400 --> 00:15:18,640
I invited you here

163
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:19,840
today...

164
00:15:20,239 --> 00:15:20,880
Your Highness,

165
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:22,559
your turn.

166
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:41,000
I lost again.

167
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:51,919
Come and play weiqi with me when you are free.

168
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,080
Thank you, Your Highness.

169
00:15:58,679 --> 00:16:00,200
Please excuse me.

170
00:16:28,039 --> 00:16:28,599
Huaping,

171
00:16:29,919 --> 00:16:31,280
what do you think of

172
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:33,280
Miss Yao?

173
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:36,479
I don't know.

174
00:16:38,919 --> 00:16:40,440
She is friendly and kind.

175
00:16:41,239 --> 00:16:42,200
I am a woman,

176
00:16:42,919 --> 00:16:44,440
but I also want to get close to her.

177
00:16:45,239 --> 00:16:46,479
Much less the Great Imperial Grandson.

178
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:48,039
Your Highness,

179
00:16:49,679 --> 00:16:51,559
do you want her to wait on His Highness?

180
00:16:53,239 --> 00:16:55,280
If someone can make His Highness happy,

181
00:16:56,119 --> 00:16:57,799
it'll be an atonement for me.

182
00:17:00,640 --> 00:17:02,320
Recite that poem again.

183
00:17:03,520 --> 00:17:04,400
Big Brother,

184
00:17:04,479 --> 00:17:06,239
didn't you say

185
00:17:06,239 --> 00:17:08,640
I don't have to weigh every word I read

186
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:10,479
but just understand the meaning?

187
00:17:10,719 --> 00:17:12,800
I don't have to sit for examinations.

188
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:14,760
Smoke rises in the desert

189
00:17:14,760 --> 00:17:15,760
and the sun sets on the river.

190
00:17:16,280 --> 00:17:17,760
Even a three-year-old can recite that.

191
00:17:18,319 --> 00:17:19,040
Look at you.

192
00:17:19,439 --> 00:17:20,319
You got so many words wrong.

193
00:17:21,319 --> 00:17:22,680
[Cooking smoke rises in the desert.]
It's not cooking smoke.

194
00:17:23,239 --> 00:17:24,760
The sun sets, not the bun.

195
00:17:25,479 --> 00:17:26,160
Big Brother,

196
00:17:26,479 --> 00:17:28,599
I drew the sunset.

197
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:29,479
Look.

198
00:17:30,079 --> 00:17:31,719
There are rays too.

199
00:17:32,560 --> 00:17:33,199
Zhu Zhanshan,

200
00:17:34,319 --> 00:17:35,640
you're making me mad.

201
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:46,439
Hurry, hurry!

202
00:17:46,439 --> 00:17:48,250
[Lantern Festival]

203
