Hurry! Hurry! Keep up.

204
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:02,800
Your Majesty.

205
00:18:08,239 --> 00:18:09,359
Your Highness.

206
00:18:09,719 --> 00:18:10,280
Grandfather,

207
00:18:11,280 --> 00:18:12,400
it's the Lantern Festival.

208
00:18:12,719 --> 00:18:14,560
The ministers are waiting to tour
Wansui Mountain with you.

209
00:18:15,040 --> 00:18:16,439
Why did you come here alone?

210
00:18:16,959 --> 00:18:19,319
The Emperor is not in the Qianqing Palace.

211
