213
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:30,760
You rode the warhorse on campaigns
for more than 10 years.

214
00:18:31,119 --> 00:18:32,319
I heard it is sick today.

215
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:35,439
I thought you would come and take a look.

216
00:18:36,319 --> 00:18:37,439
It's not sick.

217
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:40,319
It's old.

218
00:18:41,599 --> 00:18:42,119
Grandfather.

219
00:18:42,119 --> 00:18:44,400
Remember the Dragon Boat
Festival Feast that year?

220
00:18:44,959 --> 00:18:46,160
You hit the ball, shot the willow,

221
00:18:48,040 --> 00:18:49,640
and triumphed over others.

222
00:18:50,319 --> 00:18:53,839
The ministers and foreign envoys were amazed.

223
00:18:54,680 --> 00:18:56,640
