224
00:18:57,199 --> 00:19:00,319
All corners come to pay tribute in a meeting.

225
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:02,800
The second line was this:

226
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:06,160
All territories are unified
under the bright sun and moon.

227
00:19:09,359 --> 00:19:11,839
That was great.

228
00:19:13,719 --> 00:19:17,520
You behaved like a hero even at the age of 14.

229
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:35,079
Continue brushing.

230
00:19:41,719 --> 00:19:42,359
Zhanji,

231
00:19:43,599 --> 00:19:44,359
after the festival,

232
00:19:44,719 --> 00:19:47,839
get out of the palace and run an errand for me.

233
00:19:57,675 --> 00:19:59,280
[Fine Meal, Divine Work]

234
