Don't you like it?

243
00:20:59,520 --> 00:21:01,239
Qiongyuan Court has acrobatic and magic shows.

244
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:02,760
The Qiyun Club has a Cuju ball game.

245
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:03,719
It's exciting.

246
